      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start, but I need it to be even more hard-hitting. Can you write a paragraph for the introduction? I want it to really drive home the idea that ideas like \"meritocracy\" or \"equal opportunity\" are basically just excuses used to keep the status quo and ignore the reality of systemic racism. Make it sound very authoritative.",
